---
---

<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 via-white to-emerald-50 py-20 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background decoration -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-72 h-72 bg-cyan-100 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-40 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30 translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/3"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <!-- Badge -->
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-700 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
      自社開発システムで月額ツール費用0円
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
      毎月のLINEツール費用、<br class="hidden md:block" />
      もう<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-emerald-500">払わなくていい。</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      LINE公式アカウントの自動化に月額費用は不要。<br class="hidden md:block" />
      自社開発の仕組みだから、必要なのは初期構築費用だけです。
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
        </svg>
        無料相談する
      </a>
      <a href="#features" class="btn-secondary">
        機能を見る
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Trust indicators -->
    <div class="mt-14 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
      <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
        初期費用のみ
      </span>
      <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
        ベンダーロックインなし
      </span>
      <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
        最短5営業日で稼働
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
